Sour cream

00:00:10.540 --> 00:00:14.940
Preheat the oven to 180c

00:00:15.260 --> 00:00:17.500
Get the butter from the fridge. We'll need it soft later

00:00:17.500 --> 00:00:19.000
Peal the apples

00:00:24.600 --> 00:00:26.360
Cut the edges of the apple

00:00:32.680 --> 00:00:33.620
Cut it to dices

00:00:35.700 --> 00:00:37.000
In a bowl put a teaspoon of cinnamon

00:00:38.060 --> 00:00:39.240
A spoon of brown sugar

00:00:39.240 --> 00:00:41.300
And the apples

00:00:41.500 --> 00:00:42.960
And mix it

00:00:46.720 --> 00:00:47.380
Now for the cake base

00:00:47.380 --> 00:00:48.420
In a new bowl break the eggs

00:00:52.200 --> 00:00:53.100
Half a cup of oil

00:00:54.540 --> 00:00:56.020
3\4 cup of sour cream

00:00:56.360 --> 00:00:57.720
Scramble the eggs. With a fork yes?

00:00:57.980 --> 00:01:01.180
Cup and half a cup of flour

00:01:01.220 --> 00:01:02.980
Tip- straighten the flour

00:01:06.400 --> 00:01:08.200
Half a cup of sugar

00:01:09.840 --> 00:01:10.880
Mix it

