Lets continue to the crumble

00:01:33.100 --> 00:01:34.040
In a new bowl put 3\4 cup of flour

00:01:34.360 --> 00:01:35.940
Cup of sugar

00:01:36.280 --> 00:01:37.036
Cut 60g of butter

00:01:37.036 --> 00:01:39.136
How? With the measuring lines that come in the package!

00:01:41.260 --> 00:01:42.320
And to dices

00:01:44.900 --> 00:01:46.400
Try not to encounter difficulties as we did :(

00:01:48.040 --> 00:01:50.740
Mash the mixture. Dont afraid to use the hands!

00:01:55.440 --> 00:01:56.320
And put it in the oven

00:01:56.320 --> 00:01:57.580
For 50 minutes

00:02:03.980 --> 00:02:05.620
And we have an apple crumble!

